\subsection{Historic Aspect}
The site is vacant in 1900, from the history map in 1904, we can see a brick structured building was present and the building belongs to M.C Shiller. In 1959, Doherty Apartments is built [8] and has been functioning ever since. This indicates there are no major historic context needed to be reflected in the project design (\fref{fig:history}).
